    <h1>Grades</h1>
    <h3>Data from both ManageBac API (class information) and scrapy (class periods)</h3>
    <h3>(Proving that we can get pretty much ANY data out of ManageBac)</h3>    
    <h4>&nbsp;</h4>

  <table id="example" class="compact stripe order-column" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>&nbsp;</th>
                <th>Monday</th>
                <th>Tuesday</th>
                <th>Wednesday</th>
                <th>Thursday</th>
                <th>Friday</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>

        <tr tal:repeat="row rows">
            <td tal:content="python:row['name']">period</td>
            <td tal:content="python:row[1]">1</td>
            <td tal:content="python:row[2]">2</td>
            <td tal:content="python:row[3]">3</td>
            <td tal:content="python:row[4]">4</td>
            <td tal:content="python:row[5]">5</td>
        </tr>
 
        <tfoot>
            <tr>
                <th>&nbsp;</th>
                <th>Monday</th>
                <th>Tuesday</th>
                <th>Wednesday</th>
                <th>Thursday</th>
                <th>Friday</th>
            </tr>
        </tfoot>
    </table>



